        "text": "119\nthat the people should become aware of\nand contacts. When your readers\nacquainted with the idea of the brothers\nat this very moment and that every\nchance to talk to them if he becomes\nthen you may talk about my contacts\nwith G.A. Ronald, I cannot tell you\nyou must use your own judgement.\nWhen ever you feel to use it then go\nso. I am not afraid to face the people\ncomes with it, neither is Madeleine.\nUNQUOTE."
